Overall, a low time preference society is better off.

And a money that stores value into the future is key to establishing low time preference.

People are more inclined to plan for the future and make better decisions in the present.

Simply put, #bitcoin fixes this.

#Bitcoin's number go up technology lowers our time preference.

Since it appreciates over time, we would prefer to save more money today (buy bitcoin) rather than consume goods and services.

Bitcoin fixes our time preference and allows us to focus on the future.

Let's compare this to #bitcoin.

Bitcoin is a scarce digital money with a known supply and issuance schedule.

We know that there will only ever be 21M BTC, and we know how much BTC is mined daily and every day in the future.

There is a high amount of future certainty.
